However, at Farmet, they continued to invest uncompromisingly in research and development.
"We built with the endowments a training and research center, strengthened the company's presentation in international trade shows and won the main awards in national exhibitions," says Zdarsky.
Everything suggests that the crisis is behind them.
The numbers are rising and so is the number of employees.
"To the new winner I wish this pleasant feeling of victory but in a calm atmosphere," says Karel Zdarsky.
The investigation that removes foolish regulations.
The Absurdity of the Year survey is for the fourth time a part of the business clan.
Some absurd regulations have been removed.
