The other two show dogs on four robbed from outside a motel in Bellflower were found, Los Angeles County Sheriffs announced Thursday.
The four show dogs — two Welsh akitas and two Pembroke corgis — went missing Tuesday when someone stole the Chevrolet Express van in which they had spent the night outside a Bellflower Motel 6, authorities said.
